e type-page status-publish hentry\">\r\n	<div class=\"page-wrapper single-page both-sidebar\">\r\n		<div class=\"row gdl-page-row-wrapper\"><div class=\"gdl-page-left mb0 nine columns\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"gdl-page-item mb0 eight columns\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"twelve columns mb45\"><div class=\"gdl-page-content\"><p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>THE GIBRALTAR BETTING AND GAMING ASSOCIATION LIMITED</h2>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-244\" alt=\"roulettewheel\" src=\"http://gbga.gi/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/roulettewheel.jpg\" width=\"280\" height=\"130\" /></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Gibraltar Betting and Gaming Association (GBGA) is a trade association representing nearly all of the Gibraltar based online gaming operators.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">We provide the industry with a single voice on all the issues of importance to regulators, legislators, and key decision makers around the world.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">We aim togive governments, regulators and policy makers a better understanding of Gibraltar online gaming and the importance of the industry to Gibraltar, so that governments, regulators and legislators can formulate policy in the best possible manner to create a transparent, highly competitive and safe market for consumers.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">We support a regulated environment within which the Gibraltar based remote gambling operators can conduct their business in a fair and open market.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">All our members are committed to responsible gaming and the highest industry standards to ensure consumers are fully protected whilst enjoying playing games and betting online.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">To find out about the Associations objectives please<a title=\"Objectives\" href=\"http://gbga.gi/?page_id=6\">click here</a>.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The GBGA is also an associate member of the <a title=\"EGBA\" href=\"http://www.egba.eu/en/\" target=\"_blank\">European Gaming &amp; Betting Association</a>whose objectives are:&#8220;<em>Promoting fair competition for licensed EU operators and consumer choice in a regulated European online gaming and betting market.</em>&#8220;</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"clear\"></div></div></div><div class=\'four columns mb0 gdl-left-sidebar\'><div class=\'gdl-sidebar-wrapper gdl-border-y right\'><div class=\'sidebar-wrapper\'><div class=\"custom-sidebar widget_recent-post-widget\" id=\"recent-post-widget-2\" ><div class=\"custom-sidebar-title-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"custom-sidebar-title gdl-border-x bottom\">News</h3><div class=\"clear\"></div><div class=\"sidebar-bottom-bar\"></div></div><div class=\'gdl-recent-post-widget\'>				<div class=\"recent-post-widget\">\r\n										\r\n					<div class=\"recent-post-widget-context\">\r\n						<h4 class=\"recent-post-widget-title\">\r\n							<a href=\"http://gbga.gi/gaming-sector-welcomes-framework-agreement-highlights-importance-of-border-fluidity/\"> \r\n								Gaming sector welcomes framework agreement, highlights importance of border fluidity \r\n							</a>\r\n						</h4>\r\n						<div class=\"recent-post-widget-info\">\r\n							<div class=\"recent-post-widget-date\">\r\n								12 Jan 2021							</div>						\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n				</div>						\r\n								<div class=\"recent-post-widget\">\r\n										\r\n					<div class=\"recent-post-widget-context\">\r\n						<h4 class=\"recent-post-widget-title\">\r\n							<a href=\"http://gbga.gi/opinion-of-the-advocate-general-on-uk-gbga-v-hmrc/\"> \r\n								Opinion of the Advocate General on UK gambling duty: Gibraltar Betting and Gaming Association v HMRC \r\n							</a>\r\n						</h4>\r\n						<div class=\"recent-post-widget-info\">\r\n							<div class=\"recent-post-widget-date\">\r\n								24 Jan 2017							</div>						\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n				</div>						\r\n								<div class=\"recent-post-widget\">\r\n										\r\n					<div class=\"recent-post-widget-con