ue\">UPDATE DETAILS</h2><p>Once you\'re registered with GAMSTOP, it\'s important to keep your details up to date.</p><p><a class=\"button-home-blue\" id=\"update-details\" href=\"/update\">Update your details</a></p></div></div><div class=\"flex-grid grey-background heading-bar\"><h2 class=\"bordered-bottom-blue bordered-top-blue\">FURTHER SUPPORT</h2></div><div class=\"flex-grid\"><div class=\"flex-col sign-container\"><div class=\"home-sign\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"support-sign\"></div></div><div class=\"flex-col sign-line\"><p>Self-exclusion is just one way to help you restrict your online gambling activities. There are many \nother sources of support and advice to help you.</p><p><a id=\"get-support\" href=\"/support\">Get support</a></p></div></div><div class=\"flex-grid grey-background heading-bar\"><h2 class=\"bordered-bottom-blue bordered-top-blue\">Sign in to your account</h2></div><div class=\"flex-grid\"><div class=\"flex-col white-background\"><p>Sign in to your account to view the details that we currently hold for you on the Self-Exclusion register.</p><p><a id=\"sign-in\" href=\"/sign-in\">Sign in</a></p></div></div></section></article><footer><div class=\"footer-content\"><p class=\"footer-links\"><a id=\"footer-terms-of-use\" href=\"/terms-of-use\" target=\"_blank\">Terms of Use</a><a id=\"footer-privacy-policy\" href=\"/privacy-policy\" target=\"_blank\">Privacy policy</a><a id=\"footer-cookie-policy\" href=\"/cookie-policy\" target=\"_blank\">Cookie policy</a><a id=\"footer-contact-us\" href=\"/contact-us\" target=\"_blank\">Contact</a><a id=\"footer-participating-operators\" href=\"/participating-companies\" target=\"_blank\">Participating companies</a><a id=\"footer-sitemap\" href=\"/sitemap.xml\" target=\"_blank\">Sitemap</a></p><p>Copyright &copy; 2020 The National Online Self Exclusion Scheme Limited. All Rights Reserved.</p><p>The National Online Self Exclusion Scheme Limited: 3 Greengate, Cardale Park, Harrogate, HG3 1GY. Registered No. 