">Visit Group Chat</span>\n                </span></a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n              <div class=\"col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3 c-card c-card--service\">\n          <div class=\"pr-15 pr-md-0\">\n            <span class=\"c-icon mx-auto mb-10\">\n              <i class=\"fas fa-users\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>\n            </span>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"c-card__main text-md-center\">\n            <div>\n              <h3 class=\"u-h4 mb-5\">Forum</h3>\n              <p class=\"u-font-600\">The GamCare Forum is an online message board available 24/7, providing a safe and secure space to explore your situation.</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <div>\n              <a  href=\"https://www.gamcare.org.uk/forum/\"  class=\"c-btn c-btn--primary\" ><span class=\"c-pulse c-btn__pulse\"></span>\n                                <span class=\"c-btn__row\">\n                  <span class=\"c-btn__title\">Visit Forum</span>\n                </span></a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n          </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n  <section class=\"c-section-icon-cards\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <h2>Not sure youre ready to talk to someone?</h2>\n    <div class=\"row\">\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-md-6 d-flex flex-column\">\n            <a href=\"https://gamtest.se/v3/gamcare\" class=\"o-link-bare d-flex flex-column flex-fill\">\n              <div class=\"c-card c-card--icon\">\n                <div class=\"pr-xl-30 pt-xl-2\">\n                  <span class=\"c-icon c-icon--lg mx-auto mb-25 mb-xl-0\">\n                    <i class=\"fal fa-brain\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>\n                  </span>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"c-card__main text-center text-xl-left\">\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"c-card__title mb-10\">How safe is your gambling?</h3>\n                    <p class=\"u-font-600 u-line-height-sm mb-20 mb-